narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, I'd recommend ENGL127 to other students.
Yes I would recommend it, but only if you are willing to do a little bit of work.
Take this class. It's very interesting, and touches on the different aspects of the American Dream and American literature in general.
Take English 127, especially if you can get it with Professor Melina Moe. The workload is completely manageable, and the reading is more than ok if you keep up with it.
A broad survey of American literature with the intent of discovering a meaning, significance, and distinction between the ideas and styles that differentiate American Lit. from other foreign lits.
